reviews.review_text: Present and gone. Upper stand Bobby side but the Boys appeared surprisingly close.  Row Jimmy and China Doll were highlights for sure.  Awesome weekend summer tour show with rain being a theme, offering an ethereal Box of Rain  and a raucous  Aiko Aiko. 4 stars.  Hey Tapers...  Good JOB!  Thank you for this contribution.
